management algorithms using the TNM staging system.</p>", "critical_actions_en": ""}, "about": {"formula_en": "<p></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"49\" /><col width=\"164\" /><col width=\"235\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Primary tumor (T)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">TX</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Primary tumor cannot be assessed</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T0</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No evidence of primary tumor</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tis</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Carcinoma in situ</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T1</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tumor &le;2 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T1a: Tumor &le;0.5 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T1b: Tumor &gt;0.5 to &lt;1 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T1c: Tumor 1-2 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T2</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tumor &gt;2 to 4 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T3</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tumor &gt;4 cm in greatest dimension</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">T4</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tumor involves celiac axis, superior mesenteric artery, and/or common hepatic artery, regardless of size</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Regional lymph node (N)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">NX</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Regional lymph nodes cannot be assessed</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">N0</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No regional lymph node metastases</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">N1</p>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Metastasis in 1-3 regional lymph node